<br>
Verant really REALLY needs to rethink some of these things.  We have palladins all across our server who are afraid to get out of 52 so they can get a shot at the darn book for their epic.  Then we have others, who ARE above 52 and cannot use naggy as a source of this book, that are killing the other &quot;red&quot; dragons, with no books dropping.  Something needs to be done.<br>
<br>
I think it might be wise, if you feel this is wrong, to send a polite petition to our guides, so that maybe this injustice can be looked at.  I will give Verant the benefit of the doubt, and maybe realize they dont KNOW this is happening.  <br>
<br>
Sigh.<br>
<br>
Oh well, hugs all!<br>
<br>
Kalana Stormdancer<br>
58 Ranger<br>
