<br>
thx exploit<br>
<br>
Meneldil <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub28.ezboard.com/ukilmarfyrewynd.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kilmar Fyrewynd</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#993300>(6/11/01 6:37:52 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Burnt Book</span><hr size=1> Killed Talendor last week (thank CT for inviting me), and no book dropped :(<br>
<br>
Not gonna use exploit to kill dragon (yes it's a bannable offense)<br>
<br>
Paladins cannot dmg a dragon faster than the dragon can regen.<br>
<br>
And, yes Dras, I have a level 3 monkey :)<br>
<br>
-Kilmar &quot;bookless&quot; Fyrewynd, 55th Paladin of Mithaniel Marr<br>
